ZH: 我的家族是母系传承。
EN: My family lineage follows the maternal line.
ZH: 母系血统在这个家族中非常重要。
EN: The maternal lineage is very important in this family.
ZH: 她来自母系世家。
EN: She comes from a noble maternal family.
ZH: 在这个文化中，母系传统被尊重和珍视。
EN: In this culture, the maternal tradition is respected and cherished.
ZH: 母系家族的特色是强大的女性。
EN: The distinctive feature of a maternal lineage is strong women.
ZH: 母系传承可以追溯到几个世代以前。
EN: The maternal lineage can be traced back several generations.
ZH: 她对母系家族的历史深感自豪。
EN: She is proud of the history of her maternal family.
